data.description: Do you Want to be close to Fort Myers, Gateway, the interstate and shopping but want space and privacy??   Motivated Seller! Newly renovated 3 bedroom/ 2 bath/ 2 stall garages with a pool. Most if not all major items were replaced, check this home out!  Close to Fort Myers, 10 min to interstate, SWFL airport a few minutes away, privacy, but very close to town!! Stainless steel appliances, new within the last 2-3 years: a/c, water heater, septic, pool pump, water system with water softener, flooring in kitchen, living, dining, master bath, new hurricane door from master bath to pool and front door, all lighting new inside, and front lights on garage,  ceiling fans in every bedroom, new roof this year, new stainless steel sink in kitchen, new vanity in master, both toilets in baths are new, new blinds on windows, paint inside, white landscaping rock surround the home and pool area, with luminescence lighting around,  all inside doors replaced.. plus much more was done! Still able to put your own personal touches on this home to make it your own! Huge pool patio to enjoy family barbecue's or to just relax and enjoy the sun! Beautiful sunsets right from the pool patio! Nice size yard to let your pets have their space!   Great priced pool home in the area!
